                    "accordion_row_BD7YXe": {
                      "type": "_accordion-row",
                      "settings": {
                        "heading": "Why haven’t I received my order?",
                        "open_by_default": false,
                        "icon": "none",
                        "width": 20
                      },
                      "blocks": {
                        "text_PnX4xD": {
                          "type": "text",
                          "settings": {
                            "text": "<p>We know you’re looking forward to your order, and we’re here to help you track it down. There are a few reasons your delivery may be taking a little longer than expected.</p><p>Your order may still be in transit, especially during peak periods or promotional events when dispatch times can be slightly extended. It’s also worth checking your tracking details, as your parcel may be delayed with the carrier or awaiting delivery.</p><p>If your order includes multiple items, they may arrive separately depending on availability.</p><p>For the most up-to-date information, we recommend checking your shipping confirmation email or tracking link. If you still need assistance, our Customer Care team will be happy to help.</p>",
                            "width": "100%",
                            "max_width": "none",
                            "alignment": "left",
                            "type_preset": "rte",
