                      "blocks": {
                        "text_EFF6zX": {
                          "type": "text",
                          "settings": {
                            "text": "<p>You can enjoy complimentary returns by selecting the $1.98 free returns option at checkout. This ensures your item can be returned at no additional cost, avoiding standard return shipping and handling fees. If this option is not selected, returns remain available, however a $10 handling fee will apply. Please note, some items, including final sale styles, may be excluded in accordance with our returns policy.<br/><br/></p>",
